race.description: Apg Yearling Sales 3YOF Final Mobile Pace (G2)
race.comment: SOHO AMERICANO (3) had to work very hard from the back row last week but had come from there to win her previous two outings at this circuit including a Victoria Oaks triumph over several of these rivals last month. That was her second Oaks win of the season and the much better draw can see he prove her class again. The second line draw is a blow to the chances of BEACH DIAMOND (10) but she has been flying this time in with six wins and a close Oaks second to SOHO AMERICANO from seven starts. Won easily from this line here two back and has strong statistics at both the circuit and the distance. LET HER ROLL (5) has been consistent without winning of late, coming from similar draws for second in the first two rounds of the series. She was a luckless second in the 2F final last year and it wouldn't surprise to see her atone. LETS GO LORNA (2) is racing well and draws to be competitive along with ALIFETIMEFORLIVING (11) who draws on the second line but missed narrowly last week.
